OL,3,C'My beginning' was Belfast, says
OL,4,CArnold Schwarzenegger
OL,6,FActor and former governor of
OL,7,FCalifornia Arnold Schwarzenegger has
OL,8,Fbeen presented with an honorary degree
OL,9,Fduring a visit to Belfast.
OL,11,FSchwarzenegger, 78, said it was
OL,12,F"unbelievable" to be back in the city
OL,13,F60 years after his first visit.
OL,15,FThe Austrian-born star received the
OL,16,Fhonorary doctorate from Ulster
OL,17,FUniversity in recognition of his
OL,18,Fcontributions to public service,
OL,19,Fenvironmental advocacy, and the arts.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@NO]
