OL,3,C'My beginning' was Belfast, says
OL,4,CArnold Schwarzenegger
OL,6,FStudents cheered and held signs
OL,7,Freading "Ulster he's back" and "Hasta
OL,8,FLa Vista Ulster", while some brought
OL,9,Fcopies of his movie Terminator 2.
OL,11,FSchwarzenegger told those on the red
OL,12,Fcarpet rolled out for his arrival:
OL,13,F"Ulster University is a very important
OL,14,Funiversity, and it's always a great
OL,15,Fhonour to be honoured like that.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@ZO]oD@`OUpD@PO]uD@AOU
