OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774879866
OL,3,C'My beginning' was Belfast, says
OL,4,CArnold Schwarzenegger
OL,6,F"I tell you what makes this special,
OL,7,Fbecause it's kind of a 60-year
OL,8,Fanniversary and 60 years ago, in 1966
OL,9,FI was in Belfast for the first time,
OL,10,Fand there was this 19-year-old
OL,11,Fbodybuilder that was doing a posing
OL,12,Fexhibition here, because there was
OL,13,Fthis new upcoming bodybuilding
OL,14,Fchampion.
OL,16,F"So I came here, I was invited by Ivan
OL,17,FDunbar, this Irish man, I think his
OL,18,Ffamily is here... he passed away I'm
OL,19,Fsad to say, but that's where my
OL,20,Fbeginning was, in Ireland, in Belfast.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
