OL,3,C'My beginning' was Belfast, says
OL,4,CArnold Schwarzenegger
OL,6,F"And it's wonderful to be back in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland and to kind of get to
OL,8,Fsee, this is not something that I
OL,9,Fdreamt of when I was 19-years-old,
OL,10,Fwhen I was here 60 years ago, that one
OL,11,Fday I will be coming here to get an
OL,12,Fhonorary doctorate degree, it's
OL,13,Funbelievable."
